          - rid: 107151359355650060
          output: 'It was in vain; the ruffians refuse to even lend us an ear. One
            wonders how much they were paid to secure such unwavering loyalty. May
            the Beholder curse them!

            [Gained Bane Lost 10 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650061
          output: 'The scoundrels accept our offer with grins upon their faces. After
            all, we are paying them once more to perform the very same deeds they
            were already committing. A fine trade for them, but at least they are
            no longer our burden.

            [Gained 10 Bliss]

'
